                        She then walks towards the counter and scans the fish with her phone. The image recognition technology recognises the type of fish and displays it on her phone.<br/>
                        Zheng continues walking along the store shelves and spots a nice tin of tea. She wants to purchase it and scans the tea with her phone. As she shakes the phone, the tea is automatically placed into her virtual shopping cart.                        
                </p> 
