                <p>
                        <b>HEMA’s features</b><br/>
                        By analyzing HEMA’s direct competitors, we gained an understanding from our own perspective about HEMA’s key features and market strategy.<br/>
                        <b>- Brand building</b><br/>
                        HEMA builds its brand with an exquisite offline store, food with good quality and convenient delivery within 30 minutes.<br/>
                        <b>- Very wide range & Low degree of openness</b><br/>
                        HEMA’s ambition is that their customers buy all components for a meal from them. HEMA has a closed system to some extent, just like Apple, and they want to provide all the fresh groceries you need so they can replace ordinary supermarkets. Once customers buy everything they need in HEMA and they trust HEMA’s service and quality, they can form the habit of doing their entire daily shopping at HEMA.
